title: Buffy the Vampire Slayer season 9 24 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Buffy the Vampire Slayer 24

By:     	Andrew Chambliss, Karl Story, Georges Jeanty, Michelle Madsen	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Action-Adventure, Horror
Series:   	Buffy the Vampire Slayer (Variant Cover Edition)
Publisher:   	Dark Horse	
Pub. Date:  	August 14, 2013
Format:         CBZ

In a last-ditch effort to save Dawn, the heroic trio of Buffy, Willow, and Xander must split up and tackle their own demons, real and imagined. As the season's Big Bads-Severin and Simone-threaten to turn back time, the mystical council partner with Koh and Illyria to prevent a tragic tear in the fabric of time!
